      "description": "Presenting a truly remarkable, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been kept in a climate-controlled environment and reflects a level of care rarely seen on the secondary market. The exterior paint retains its original factory depth and luster, free of swirl marks, rock chips, or any imperfections. Every panel gap is precise, and the trim remains dark and supple. Inside, the cabin is a time capsule: the premium leather seats are firm and uncreased, the carpets are spotless, and it retains that distinct new-car scent. All electronics, switches, and displays function perfectly with no wear on the touchpoints. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; the engine bay is detailed to a mirror finish, and the vehicle comes with a comprehensive folder of every service performed since mile one. This is not just a used car",
